	(text "Shunt regulator / brake chopper.\n48V mode: trip 51.4V, release ~50.4V. \n24V mode: trip 27.4V, release ~26.2V.\nNever move mode switch while powered. \nDump: Arcol HS100 4R7 100W on heatsink via J17 + KSD9700-70 NC thermal switch. Supply OVP must exceed trip voltage."
